        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Nora\nGuest: Daniel Cho\n#fixture-v3: failure_modes=high_person_density\n#fixture-v3: voice=en-US host_voice=en-US\nNora: Welcome back to Long Horizon Notes."
      },
